    "longBusinessSummary": "Duc Thanh Wood Processing Joint Stock Company manufactures, sells, and trades in wooden kitchenware, household utensils, home furniture, children's toys, and other products. The company offers kitchenware, including cutting boards, trivets, bread cutting boards and bread boxes, trays, coasters and mug trees, spice racks, wooden spoons and forks, salad bowls, and other products; housewares, such as magazine racks, CD and DVD racks, wine racks, key holders, cloth hangers, and other products; and in-door furniture products. In addition, it manufactures kid's toys made of rubber wood, MDF, and plywood. The company distributes its products through points of sale; shopping centers; and showroom in Vietnam. It exports its products to 50 countries, including Asia, Europe, and the United States. Duc Thanh Wood Processing Joint Stock Company was founded in 1991 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
